        "##**Feature Engineering**"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 49,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "wmEIRZ40wH2f"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "df[\"balanceDiffOrig\"] = df[\"newbalanceOrig\"] - df[\"oldbalanceOrg\"]\n",
        "df[\"balanceDiffDest\"] = df[\"newbalanceDest\"] - df[\"oldbalanceDest\"]"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 50,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "Wu2t1SnPZscu"
      },
      "outputs": [
        {
          "name": "stdout",
          "output_type": "stream",
          "text": [
            "0\n"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "source": [
        "mask_no_activity = (\n",
        "    (df[\"amount\"] == 0) & # This condition will always be False now.\n",
        "    (df[\"balanceDiffOrig\"] == 0) &\n",
        "    (df[\"balanceDiffDest\"] == 0)\n",
        ")\n",
        "print(mask_no_activity.sum())"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "nEP-MIKAwM9y"
      },
      "source": [
        "Mengukur perubahan saldo sebelum dan sesudah transaksi. <br>\n",
        "balanceDiffOrig untuk perubahan saldo pengirim <br>\n",
        "balanceDiffDest untuk perubahan saldo penerima"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 51,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "G4gFU-0QwbRK"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "df[\"isDestMerchant\"] = (df[\"nameDest\"].str.startswith(\"M\")).astype(int)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 52,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "u2cZjOpEwkf6"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "df.drop(columns=[\"nameDest\"], inplace=True)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "LMjm0UYgwezH"
      },
      "source": [
        "Menandai apakah tujuan transaksi adalah merchant atau bukan."
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "7NEDrcDpwn_M"
      },
      "source": [
        "Karena data sudah disimpan di isDestMerchant, jadi ID unik yang digunakan tidak dipakai lagi"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 53,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "dr4fp0jIwyMP"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "df[\"origDrainedToZero\"] = ((df[\"oldbalanceOrg\"] > 0) & (df[\"newbalanceOrig\"] == 0)).astype(int)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "erRTD9J6wz6L"
      },
      "source": [
        "Menandai apakah akun pengirim dikuras habis <br>\n",
        "oldbalanceOrg > 0 untuk sebelumnya ada uang <br>\n",
        "newbalanceOrig == 0 untuk setelah transaksi jadi nol <br>\n",
        "Karena Fraud sering menguras saldo sampai habis"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 54,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "1nHx52KXxFHL"
      },
      "outputs": [
        {
          "data": {
            "text/plain": [
              "origDrainedToZero\n",
              "0    0.000038\n",
              "1    0.005269\n",
              "Name: isFraud, dtype: float64"
            ]
          },
          "execution_count": 54,
          "metadata": {},
          "output_type": "execute_result"
        }
      ],
      "source": [
        "df.groupby(\"origDrainedToZero\")[\"isFraud\"].mean()"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "IE6NsfFSxHuP"
      },
      "source": [
        "Mengelompokkan data berdasarkan origDrainedToZero (0 atau 1) dan menghitung rata-rata isFraud, 1 artinya fraud tinggi, 0 artinya fraud rendah"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "kGHViRUD1MaQ"
      },
      "source": [
        "### **ENTROPY ANALYSIS**"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 55,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "Hs8RUtgC1buP"
      },
      "outputs": [
        {
          "name": "stdout",
          "output_type": "stream",
          "text": [
            "amount               : 0.017\n",
            "oldbalanceOrg        : 0.419\n",
            "newbalanceOrig       : 0.475\n",
            "oldbalanceDest       : 0.033\n",
            "newbalanceDest       : 0.038\n",
            "isFraud              : 0.010\n",
            "step                 : 2.486\n",
            "isDestMerchant : 0.640\n",
            "type: 1.308\n"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "source": [
        "from scipy.stats import entropy as scipy_entropy\n",
        "\n",
        "numeric_cols = ['amount', 'oldbalanceOrg', 'newbalanceOrig',\n",
        "                'oldbalanceDest', 'newbalanceDest', 'isFraud', 'step']\n",
        "\n",
        "def discrete_entropy(series):\n",
        "  counts = series.value_counts(normalize=True)\n",
        "  return scipy_entropy(counts)\n",
        "\n",
        "ent_res = {}\n",
        "for col in numeric_cols:\n",
        "  binned = pd.cut(df[col].astype(float), bins=20)\n",
        "  ent_res[col] = discrete_entropy(binned)\n",
        "  print(f\"{col:20s} : {ent_res[col]:.3f}\")\n",
        "\n",
        "#categorical cols\n",
        "ent_res['isDestMerchant'] = discrete_entropy(df['isDestMerchant'])\n",
        "print(f\"isDestMerchant : {ent_res['isDestMerchant']:.3f}\")\n",
        "ent_res['type']= discrete_entropy(df['type'])\n",
        "print(f'type: {ent_res[\"type\"]:.3f}')"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "qPT3BfGK5Z8L"
      },
      "source": [
        "Mengecek entropy untuk mengukur seberapa acak suatu data. Nilai entropy yang tinggi menunjukkan bahwa data variatif dan acak, sedangkan entropy rendah menggambarkan bahwa data seragam."
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "SOur29dI6I1Q"
      },
      "source": [
        "### **Data Transformation**"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 56,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "kYw7BsJt6IdN"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "type_dummies = pd.get_dummies(df[\"type\"], prefix=\"type\")\n",
        "df = pd.concat([df.drop(columns=[\"type\"]), type_dummies], axis=1)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "55na4myU7R6G"
      },
      "source": [
        "Mengubah kolom type jadi beberapa kolom biner, hapus kolom lama, gabung hasil encoding"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 57,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "UuPzgJJlNIqs"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "from sklearn.preprocessing import RobustScaler\n",
        "\n",
        "scale_cols = [\n",
        "    \"amount\", \"oldbalanceOrg\", \"oldbalanceDest\",\n",
        "    \"balanceDiffOrig\", \"balanceDiffDest\", \"step\"\n",
        "]\n",
        "\n",
        "scaler = RobustScaler()\n",
        "df[scale_cols] = scaler.fit_transform(df[scale_cols])\n",
        "cleaning_log.append(\"Applied RobustScaler : Digunakan karena data memiliki banyak outlier ekstrem pada amount\")"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "HR9b9S6L70G1"
      },
      "source": [
        "Scalling digunakan untuk menyamakan semua skala fitur agar tidak ada fitur yang mendominasi dan menyebabkan bias pada hasil clustering. Dengan scalling semua fitur punya pengaruh yang adil. scaling (normalisasi) fitur numerik, khususnya supaya model tidak “terganggu” oleh nilai yang sangat besar atau outlier."
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "J-HPrxAy-X9J"
      },
      "source": [
        "### **Feature Selection**"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 58,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "ca2qTLbPCH3C"
      },
